_sText:
Map was made for server "sex with zombie" on -miCk0-'s request.
The secrets and map overview can be seen in this video: [CLICK ME](http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QPGtbI_VHoM "The video")

It took me like 4 days to make, but I was mapping only like 2/1 hour(s) a day.

Here is what is inside the map:

- 1 small easter egg
- House with 2 floors and basement
- Standalone basement outside the house
- Some custom decals
- Another, but small locked room outside (password - 1374)
- Hidden USP that will make you faster when you hold it
- Hidden AWP
- Hidden machine gun
- Hidden auto-shotgun
